Which Attributes

Source: R/bugphyzz.R
whichAttr.Rd

whichAttr shows which attributes are present in a dataset imported with importBugphyzz. This would be the names of the singatures created with getBugphyzzSignatures.

whichAttr(bp)

Arguments

bp

A data.frame imported with importBugphyzz.

Value

A character vector.

Examples


bp <- importBugphyzz()
#> Using data downloaded on 2023-07-17 14:21:22.
#> Warning: The following named parsers don't match the column names: BacDive_ID, Type_strain, PATRIC_ID
whichAttr(bp)
